ires MTP, so I need to add these properties to switch to the MSTest runner.\n\nFor hang dump support, I'll also need to add the `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.HangDump` package.","outputTokens":672,"requestId":"7683:2F696B:F8B8:130BD:69F2AC53"},"id":"eb013779-38e1-4268-9344-0c6ffb6240d0","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:12:03.028Z","parentId":"3b66ca4a-db42-45af-b3a8-e01590b7c015"}
